precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a TREATY ON
MUTUAL ASSISTANCE IN CRIMINAL MATTERS between Canada and the State of
ISRAEL, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing other
officials to sign the Treaty on behalf of Canada.
